## 7. Troubleshooting

| Symptom | Likely cause / fix |
|---|---|
| `FileNotFoundError: ..._encoder.onnx` in sim | Field graph has no encoder companion. Re-export the checkpoint (§3). |
| `Invalid rank for input: y0` | Feeding the encoder a 2-D array. The graphs are rank-1; the current sim already feeds 1-D. |
| `X has 6 features, but StandardScaler is expecting 5` | State-size mismatch. The sim derives `state_size` from the encoder input width; confirm you passed the correct field graph and scaler. |
| `vstack ... size 7 vs 6` in the geodesic branch | Frame-width mismatch; ensure you're on the integrated-frame reverse transform passing the full `[:, 0:6]`. |
| `state[:, 4] index out of bounds` (reverse transform) | The reverse transform needs the **time** column; pass `NEXT_extrap[:, 0:6]`, not `[:, 1:6]`. |
| Extrapolations explode after impact | Should be fixed by the stop-time bound. Confirm the impact guide point loaded (no fallback warning) and `--sub-steps 4`. |
| `[warn] could not load impact guide point ...` | The `<target>/impact/<file>` sibling is missing; the frame origin falls back to the glide file's last row and may be slightly off. Provide the impact file or verify the phase-library layout. |
| Double "GRU-ODE detected" banner | A stale duplicate setup block — the shipped file has only one; ensure you didn't reintroduce it. |

