| File | Role |
|---|---|
| `NEXT_training.py` (`..._grdth_heun.py`) | Trains the model; sliding-window support; exports ONNX (field + encoder) at end of run. |
| `gru_ode.py` | GRU-ODE cells, `GRUODEFunc` (encoder/decoder + coupled cell), `GRUODEPredictorModel` (stateless `[y,h]` field). |
